e
e(n)
e=1 + \frac{1}{1!} + \frac{1}{2!} + \frac{1}{3!} + \ldots
e(n) = 1 + \frac{1}{1!} + \frac{1}{2!} + \frac{1}{3!} + \ldots + \frac{1}{n!}
e(n-1) = 1 + \frac{1}{1!} + \frac{1}{2!} + \frac{1}{3!} + \ldots + \frac{1}{(n-1)!}
e(n) - e(n-1) = 1 + \frac{1}{1!} + \frac{1}{2!} + \frac{1}{3!} + \ldots + \frac{1}{n!} - \Big(1 + \frac{1}{1!} + \frac{1}{2!} + \frac{1}{3!} + \ldots + \frac{1}{(n-1)!}\Big) = \frac{1}{n!}.
e(n) - e(n-1) = \frac{1}{n!}
= \frac{1}{n!}
e(n) - e(n-1) = \frac{1}{n!}
e(n) = e(n-1) + \frac{1}{n!}
